					The remaining part of this paper unfolds as follows: In Sect.
					2, we restate the pointwise estimates of the stationary solution which have been derived in [
					39]. Next, for reader’s convenience, we recall the properties of the smoothed rarefaction waves which have been constructed in [
					7,
					26,
					41]. In Sect.
					3, the original problem is reformulated and our main theorem is also restated. Section
					4 is devoted to establishing the a priori estimates for the reformulated problem. Finally, in Sect.
					5, we present the proof of our main Theorem
					1.1.

